  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Peel and mince the garlic, then mix with coconut oil, salt, and black pepper in a small bowl.",
    "Place the garlic mixture in a ramekin and roast in the preheated oven for 15 minutes, or until the garlic is tender and lightly browned.",
    "Meanwhile, puree the apple, mustard seeds, and jalapeno pepper in a blender until smooth.",
    "Add the honey, coconut aminos, cilantro, ginger, and crushed red pepper to the blender and blend until well combined.",
    "After the garlic has roasted, remove it from the oven and brush with the glaze.",
    "Return the garlic to the oven and roast for an additional 5 minutes, or until the glaze is caramelized.",
    "Remove the garlic from the oven and let cool slightly before serving.",
    "Garnish with additional cilantro if desired."
  ],
